{"tid":1852043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衛生署狠狠摑元秋一大巴：外科口罩用完即棄  千祈咪洗咪蒸重用","createTime":"2020-01-30T09:24:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T09:44:05.000Z","uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"794ea70bd550d639aa5f9cf9c7ec5fb1b40a6bd6","tid":1852043,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:24:23.000Z","msg":"【外科口罩用完即棄  千祈咪洗咪蒸重用】<br />\n<br />\n外科口罩洗完蒸完就可以再用?! 唔好信呢啲謠言啦！<br />\n<br />\n所有外科口罩都係即棄式，用完除落嚟就要對摺棄置喺有蓋垃圾桶內，然後潔手。 <br />\n<br />\n用過嘅口罩表面已經沾染病菌，唔可以袋埋再用!而且濕咗嘅口罩會影響效用，千祈咪隨便相信網上非可靠來源嘅訊息！<br />\n<br />\n有關「嚴重新型傳染性病原體呼吸系統病」嘅最新健康資訊，快啲睇衞生防護中心嘅專題網頁:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chp.gov.hk/tc/features/102465.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ffeatures%2F102465.html&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinAxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=0d649a2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.chp.gov.hk/tc/features/102465.html</a><br />\n<br />\n#同心抗疫 #預防肺炎 #預防呼吸道傳染病 #外科口罩 #用完即棄 #潔手 #抗疫資訊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/975074992508418/posts/3280700895279138/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F975074992508418%2Fposts%2F3280700895279138%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinAxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=cb053758\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/975074992508418/posts/3280700895279138/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"e304d7c6f95df2793690d05ba02ff806f3559ab3","tid":1852043,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1f756c820b468a4d7def2d4bedc012debf4b3d","tid":1852043,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:26:10.000Z","msg":"現任立法會衞生事務委員會主席：蔣麗芸議員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.g